.git
.gitignore
.dockerignore
Dockerfile
docker-compose.yml
docs/
# Exclude the bulk of media/ — user-uploaded course / category galleries
# get to ~350MB+ committed and used to ship as docker build context on
# every push, failing the deploy (silent build.sh exit 255). All catalog
# product/category images are served from Cloudflare R2 at runtime so
# they don't need to be in the image.
#
# Re-include the small theme-baked subdirs (wysiwyg banners, email logo,
# favicon, root .htaccess) via negation — these are referenced by static
# templates/CMS blocks and must be present at /media/ path on the
# webserver. Total re-included: ~1MB.
media/
!media/.htaccess
!media/wysiwyg/
!media/wysiwyg/**
!media/email/
!media/email/**
!media/favicon/
!media/favicon/**
!media/whatsapp.png

# Re-exclude Ultimo *demo* media that the broad `!media/wysiwyg/**` negation
# above would otherwise pull back into the image. These are theme demo assets
# (sample patterns/backgrounds/swatches/slideshow), not live brand assets, and
# were removed from the media volume to reclaim space. Keep them out of builds.
# (Order matters: last-matching pattern wins, so these must follow the negation.)
media/wysiwyg/infortis/
media/wysiwyg/demo/
media/wysiwyg/swatches/
# Magento WYSIWYG media-browser thumbnail cache — regenerated on demand by the
# CMS image manager, never referenced by the storefront. ~7MB of pure cache the
# `!media/wysiwyg/**` negation would otherwise bake into the image.
media/wysiwyg/.thumbs/

# The dirs below live under media/ and are therefore ALREADY excluded by the
# blanket `media/` rule above (no `!` negation re-includes them) — they cannot
# bloat the build today. Listed explicitly only to document intent and guard
# against a future broad negation accidentally pulling them in:
#   media/dhl/         — DHL shipping module images (no shipping in this LMS)
#   media/downloadable/ — Magento downloadable-product samples (unused)
#   media/providers/   — legacy provider logos (2013-era, orphaned)
#   media/trainers/    — legacy trainer banner (orphaned; trainer photos live in wysiwyg/)
media/dhl/
media/downloadable/
media/providers/
media/trainers/

# IDE and OS files
.idea/
.vscode/
.DS_Store

# Temporary and cache files
var/cache/
var/session/
var/log/
var/report/
var/tmp/

# Node modules
node_modules/
